Package csw.command.client

Class CRMCacheProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.command.client.CRMCacheProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, scala.Equals, scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    public class CRMCacheProperties
extends java.lang.Object
implements scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Configurations to be used by underlying CommandResponseState's cache maintained by CommandResponseManagerActor

    param: maxSize maximum number of states the cache can hold, used for eviction of states param: expiry maximum amount of time a state can stay in cache from last access, also used for eviction
